---
title: Apricot-Balsamic Duck Breasts with Rosemary Roasted Potatoes
description: Duck and fruit are made for each other! We've paired duck breasts with a balsamic-apricot sauce for a tangy-sweet flavour combination. Rosemary-roasted potatoes bring earthy richness, while a fresh side salad lightens the plate!
